<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFPlutarch1973">Plutarch, Ian Scott-Kilvert (1973). <i><a href="http://books.google.co.in/books?id=Lnur0BjQO2oC&amp;pg=PA257&amp;dq=Alexander+Philoneicus+Thessaly&amp;ei=yQGySYmzKpK4Np3PqNoL&amp;client=firefox-a" class="external text" title="http://books.google.co.in/books?id=Lnur0BjQO2oC&amp;pg=PA257&amp;dq=Alexander+Philoneicus+Thessaly&amp;ei=yQGySYmzKpK4Np3PqNoL&amp;client=firefox-a" rel="nofollow">The Age of Alexander</a></i>. Penguin Classics. p.&#160;257. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0140442863" class="internal">ISBN 0140442863</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.co.in/books?id=Lnur0BjQO2oC&amp;pg=PA257&amp;dq=Alexander+Philoneicus+Thessaly&amp;ei=yQGySYmzKpK4Np3PqNoL&amp;client=firefox-a" class="external free" title="http://books.google.co.in/books?id=Lnur0BjQO2oC&amp;pg=PA257&amp;dq=Alexander+Philoneicus+Thessaly&amp;ei=yQGySYmzKpK4Np3PqNoL&amp;client=firefox-a" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.co.in/books?id=Lnur0BjQO2oC&amp;pg=PA257&amp;dq=Alexander+Philoneicus+Thessaly&amp;ei=yQGySYmzKpK4Np3PqNoL&amp;client=firefox-a</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Age+of+Alexander&amp;rft.aulast=Plutarch&amp;rft.aufirst=Ian+Scott-Kilvert&amp;rft.au=Plutarch%2C+Ian+Scott-Kilvert&amp;rft.date=1973&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B257&amp;rft.pub=Penguin+Classics&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.co.in%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DLnur0BjQO2oC%26pg%3DPA257%26dq%3DAlexander%2BPhiloneicus%2BThessaly%26ei%3DyQGySYmzKpK4Np3PqNoL%26client%3Dfirefox-a&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexander_the_Great"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-48LawsPower350-21">^ <a href="#cite_ref-48LawsPower350_21-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-48LawsPower350_21-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-48LawsPower350_21-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFGreene2000">Greene, Robert (2000). <i><a href="/wiki/The_48_Laws_of_Power" title="The 48 Laws of Power">The 48 Laws of Power</a></i>. <a href="/wiki/Penguin_Books" title="Penguin Books">Penguin Books</a>. pp.&#160;350. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0140280197" class="internal">ISBN 0140280197</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%5B%5BThe+48+Laws+of+Power%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Greene&amp;rft.aufirst=Robert&amp;rft.au=Greene%2C+Robert&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B350&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BPenguin+Books%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0140280197&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Alexander_the_Great"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22" title="">^</a></b> Other sources claim that he died of wounds sustained in a battle in <a href="/wiki/Pakistan" title="Pakistan">Pakistan</a>.</li>
