<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFTrudy_Ring.2C_Robert_M._Salkin.2C_K._A._Berney.2C_Paul_E._Schellinger1994">Trudy Ring, Robert M. Salkin, K. A. Berney, Paul E. Schellinger (1994). <a href="/wiki/Taylor_%26_Francis" title="Taylor &amp; Francis" class="mw-redirect">Taylor &amp; Francis</a>. ed. <i><a href="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC" class="external text" title="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC" rel="nofollow">International dictionary of historic places</a></i>. pp.&#160;<a href="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC&amp;pg=PA49&amp;vq=alexander+egypt+persian+liberator&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" class="external text" title="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC&amp;pg=PA49&amp;vq=alexander+egypt+persian+liberator&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" rel="nofollow">49</a>, <a href="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC&amp;pg=PA320&amp;vq=alexander+egypt+persian+liberator&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" class="external text" title="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC&amp;pg=PA320&amp;vq=alexander+egypt+persian+liberator&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" rel="nofollow">320</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781884964036" class="internal">ISBN 978-1884964036</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC" class="external free" title="http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.es/books?id=2aOpeBnbxvsC</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=International+dictionary+of+historic+places&amp;rft.aulast=Trudy+Ring%2C+Robert+M.+Salkin%2C+K.+A.+Berney%2C+Paul+E.+Schell