</ul>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-grimal-29">^ <a href="#cite_ref-grimal_29-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-grimal_29-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFNicolas_Grimal1992">Nicolas Grimal (1992). Blackwell Publishing. ed. <i><a href="http://books.google.es/books?id=GzTiXt49I0YC&amp;pg=PA382&amp;vq=alexander&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" class="external text" title="http://books.google.es/books?id=GzTiXt49I0YC&amp;pg=PA382&amp;vq=alexander&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" rel="nofollow">A History of Ancient Egypt</a></i> (reprint ed.). p.&#160;382. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780631193960" class="internal">ISBN 978-0631193960</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.es/books?id=GzTiXt49I0YC&amp;pg=PA382&amp;vq=alexander&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" class="external free" title="http://books.google.es/books?id=GzTiXt49I0YC&amp;pg=PA382&amp;vq=alexander&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.es/books?id=GzTiXt49I0YC&amp;pg=PA382&amp;vq=alexander&amp;dq=persian+egypt+%22Alexander+the+Great+%22&amp;hl=ca&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;cad=0</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+History+of+Ancient+Egypt&amp;rft.aulast=Nicolas+Grimal&amp;rft.au=Nicolas+Grimal&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.pages=p.%26nbsp%3B382&amp;rft.edition=reprint&amp;rft.isbn=978-0631193960&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.es%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DGzTiXt49I0YC%26pg%3DPA382%26vq%3Dalexander%26dq%3Dpersian%2Begypt%2B%2522Alexander%2Bthe%2BGreat%2B%2522%26hl%3Dca%26source%3Dgbs_search_s%26cad%3D0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.or